products.title: Tropical Greens
products.product_description: A vibrant blend of pineapple, mango, and spinach with a hint of coconut water. Packed with vitamins and minerals to boost your energy and immunity while tasting like a tropical vacation.

products.title: Berry Beet Blast
products.product_description: A powerful antioxidant blend of mixed berries, beetroot, and chia seeds. This deep red smoothie supports circulation and heart health while delivering a naturally sweet berry flavor.

products.title: Golden Turmeric Latte
products.product_description: A warming blend of turmeric, black pepper, coconut milk, and dates. This golden elixir offers anti-inflammatory benefits with a creamy, lightly spiced flavor profile.

products.title: Chocolate Avocado Mousse
products.product_description: A decadent yet healthy dessert made with ripe avocados, raw cacao, and maple syrup. Rich in healthy fats and antioxidants, this creamy mousse satisfies chocolate cravings guilt-free.

products.title: Pumpkin Spice Oatmeal
products.product_description: Seasonal comfort in a bowl featuring pumpkin puree, warming spices, gluten-free oats, and pecans. Packed with fiber and vitamin A to support immunity through colder months.

products.title: Matcha Green Energy
products.product_description: Premium ceremonial matcha blended with spinach, banana, and almond butter. Provides sustained energy and focus without the crash, packed with antioxidants and L-theanine.

products.title: Salted Caramel Protein Bites
products.product_description: Decadent bites with dates, almond butter, and a hint of sea salt. Each piece delivers plant-based protein and healthy fats to satisfy sweet cravings while supporting muscle recovery.

products.title: Chia Pudding Trio
products.product_description: Three layers of chia pudding featuring vanilla bean, mixed berries, and dark chocolate. Rich in omega-3s and fiber, this parfait-style breakfast keeps you full for hours.
